# TripiAgent — Code rules

Follow `.cursor/rules/tripiagent-project-contract.mdc` for stack and workflow.

- API routes: Zod-validate inputs; never expose `GEMINI_*` or `GOOGLE_*` or `OPENWEATHER_*` in client bundles.
- Rate limit `/api/ai` (document serverless in-memory limitation).
- PWA plugin: production only.
- No Vercel SPA rewrite of all routes to /.
- **Local Dev Port**: 9001 only — http://localhost:9001.
